    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 50-53.</p><p>Ki-Borne Awareness</p><p>At 22nd level, you learn to use your Focus to pierce through any illusion and detect those that are hidden. As a bonus action on your turn, you can expend 3 Focus points to gain truesight out to a range of 30 feet.</p><p>You can expend additional Focus points beyond the initial 3 to extend the range by 10 feet per additional Focus point expended as part of the same bonus action. This feature lasts for a minute or until you are incapacitated.</p></div>",
